<ul><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OlderThanRadio" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OlderThanRadio">Older Than Radio</a>: One youth in Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix's famous 1830 painting <em><a class="urllink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberty_Leading_the_People">Liberty Leading the People<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a></em> (<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NippleAndDimed" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NippleAndDimed">somewhat</a> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NSFW" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NSFW">NSFW</a>) picturing the July Revolution of the same year.
